---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About Techo</h1>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Founded in 2014, Techo has been at the forefront of technological innovation, helping businesses transform and thrive in the digital age. Our journey began with a simple mission: to make advanced technology accessible and beneficial for businesses of all sizes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Today, we're proud to be trusted by hundreds of companies worldwide, delivering cutting-edge solutions that drive growth and efficiency.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          To empower businesses through innovative technical solutions that drive growth, efficiency, and success in the digital age.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We constantly push boundaries to deliver cutting-edge solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We strive for the highest quality in everything we do.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Integrity</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We build trust through honest and transparent relationships.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>